subSubSection.paragraph:
Chromosome number
:—2n = 14 (
Benedì & Orell 1992b
); 2n = 18 (
Vignal & Reynaud 1992
); n = 9 (
Vignal & Reynaud 1992
).

Ecology
:—Nitrophyte proper to ruderal communities of trampled biotopes (
Benedì & Orell 1992a
). It is reported as species that colonize rocky hillsides, gravel plains, saline and sandy soils, fields, gardens and roadsides (
Pahlevani & Riina 2011
).
